				<h2>Info for Artists</h2>
				
				<p>The EAC Over-60s Art Awards are open to all artists over the age of 60, resident anywhere in the world. Works in all mediums  - 2D and 3D - are accepted, and must have been completed in the last 3 years, and since the artist reached the age of 60. There are no restrictions on subject matter.</p>
				<p>Artists may submit up to five works for the competition, either online or by post. <a href="#">Online entry</a> is by completion of the online form and the upload of jpeg images.</p>
				
				<p><a href="#">Postal entry</a> is by submission of the downloaded/printed entry form along with colour photographs or A4 print reproductions.</p> 

				<h5>Entry Fee</h5>
				
				<p>The entry fee is £5 per work.<br>Online payment is by Paypal or credit card.<br>Postal payment is by cheque, made payable to EAC Art Awards.</p>
				
